thread.title_full: Jerry Cesak of "Jeff & Jer" radio duo retiring - CBS News 8 - San Diego, CA News Station - KFMB Channel 8

author: Video Report By Steve Price, Reporter
title: Jerry Cesak of "Jeff & Jer" radio duo retiring
text:
SAN DIEGO (CBS 8) - Wednesday was the last time on air for longtime San Diego radio personality Jerry Cesak who is retiring after a decades long career in broadcasting.
Cesak was half of San Diego's notorious "Jeff & Jer" dynamic radio duo. He announced his retirement last month, stating that October 14th would be his last show on KyXy 96.5.
CBS News 8's Steve Price has the details in this video story.
